Fastly

Let's understand- The word 'Fastly' does not exist. The correct word is 'Fast' which is both an adjective and an adverb. 
Utkarsh is a fast runner (adjective).
Utkarsh runs fast (adverb).

Incorrect Usage-  He was asked to complete the task fastly.

Correct usage-     He was asked to complete the task fast. (Quickly can also be used here)
